name: 99Bottles
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ninety nine bottles
des:
Entertain or annoy your friends and family by having Alexa sing 99 Bottles of Beer on the wall! Every now and then she will stop to ask if she should keep singing. Have her sing to your heart's content!

To launch, simply say, "Alexa, open 99 bottles."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
